1
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:33,290
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,310 --> 00:00:36,290
[Episode 12: The Tempting Wish Fox]

3
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,120
Can you draw him or not?

4
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,010
It's been a whole night.

5
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:26,430
Or was there never such a person,

6
00:01:27,230 --> 00:01:30,289
and this is all just an excuse
for you to get away with it?

7
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:31,950
No.

8
00:01:32,350 --> 00:01:33,280
That's not true.

9
00:01:33,479 --> 00:01:33,870
I...

10
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:35,920
I remember his eyes.

11
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:37,350
His eyes looked like this.

12
00:01:37,350 --> 00:01:39,039
And his mouth was like this.

13
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:42,570
But somehow when I put it together,
it just feels off.

14
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:45,350
Maybe I was too drunk that night.

15
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,229
The memory has already become blurred.

16
00:01:48,229 --> 00:01:49,690
Hurry up and think harder.

17
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,450
Is it him?

18
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:22,620
Yes, it's him.

19
00:02:23,010 --> 00:02:24,410
Right, that's him!

20
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,910
Lady Fufeng.

21
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,660
How could you draw it so exactly like him?

22
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:31,140
Send this portrait
to the county yamen at once.

23
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:32,680
Hand it personally to Bai Shanjun.

24
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,560
Tell him,

25
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:34,780
if he encounters this demon,

26
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:36,300
he must not speak to him,

27
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:39,360
and absolutely
can't agree to any of his requests.

28
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,560
This demon is extremely dangerous.

29
00:02:42,829 --> 00:02:43,560
Yes, Master.

30
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:49,200
[Dedication Above Self]

31
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:51,150
Where is Lord Bai?

32
00:02:51,630 --> 00:02:53,829
Lady Fufeng has urgent news to tell him.

33
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:55,800
Deputy Magistrate Shi!

34
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,680
Where is Lord Bai?

35
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:02,430
Miss Fengling.

36
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:03,740
Lord Bai is...

37
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,980
He and Constable Chen

38
00:03:05,980 --> 00:03:09,090
took the men out early this morning.

39
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:12,520
They said they received a new lead,

40
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:17,360
so they're searching the whole town
for the scholar in white from the drawing.

41
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,280
The scholar in white?

42
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,030
Yes.

43
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:22,630
They said it was a new lead provided
by the leopard cat demon.

44
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:25,910
It's that suspicious man
he saw at the Li residence.

45
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:28,120
Well,

46
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:36,500
it's the one drawn
in the student's painting.

47
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,130
They're in trouble!

48
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:44,700
You two.

49
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:45,960
Sir,

50
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:46,960
two bowls of tea.

51
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:49,000
Coming right up.

52
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,460
Sorry to keep you waiting.

53
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,079
Here's your tea.

54
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:53,710
Enjoy.

55
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:54,800
Take care.

56
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,940
According to what Li Mao said,

57
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:59,810
the scholar in white
should be somewhere nearby.

58
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,630
This area isn't small.

59
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:04,040
We may be searching for quite some time.

60
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:07,630
My Lord, let me see.

61
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:23,430
Speak.

62
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,800
Tell me your wish.

63
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,720
Was he sitting here a moment ago?

64
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,050
Let's go take a look.

65
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,290
Don't be afraid.

66
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:40,830
Tell me your wish.

67
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,730
I will make it come true for you.

68
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,190
Sir,

69
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:46,480
we suspect

70
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,560
you may be connected
to a murder case in town.

71
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,190
Please come back to county yamen with us

72
00:04:50,190 --> 00:04:52,050
and assist in the investigation.

73
00:04:52,370 --> 00:04:53,500
Is that so?

74
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,940
I have nothing to hide
and fear no shadows.

75
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:59,800
Of course I'm willing
to cooperate with you both...

76
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,820
to prove my innocence.

77
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:03,390
Hu.

78
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:23,830
He's not human.

79
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:25,870
What?

80
00:05:26,450 --> 00:05:28,080
Did you sense his demonic aura?

81
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,300
My Lord, that's what you don't understand.

82
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:31,120
In Yin-Yang Crossing,

83
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:33,630
the real powerful demons
carry no demonic aura at all.

84
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:34,630
Look at how he walks—

85
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:35,600
his feet never stir a speck of dust,

86
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,000
and his steps make no sound.

87
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,360
There's not a single
drop of dew clings to his robes.

88
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,360
And after walking all this way,

89
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,620
as a scholar, he isn't even out of breath.

90
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:53,230
You're right.

91
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,960
You two officials
must be quite burdened with duties.

92
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,560
Such an exhausting journey,

93
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:00,000
surely there's something you want, right?

94
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:03,830
For example, soaring in the sky

95
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:06,160
to be spared the hardship of travel.

96
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:08,040
Why didn't you say you can fly earlier?

97
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:10,310
My feet are killing me,
walking down this road.

98
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,170
Stop chatting.

99
00:06:11,490 --> 00:06:12,490
Focus on the road.

100
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,800
And you, handsome young magistrate.

101
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,660
What about you?

102
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,920
What is it that you desire?

103
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:25,950
Do you want people to believe in you?

104
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:28,280
Do you want to be respected,

105
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:29,430
or

106
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,600
to no longer be alone?

107
00:06:36,270 --> 00:06:37,430
I desire nothing.

108
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,850
Save your tricky words.

109
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:39,830
No.

110
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,380
You do want something.

111
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:44,800
Say it.

112
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,970
I can make it come true for you.

113
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:48,560
I'll say it again.

114
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:50,080
I don't have any wishes.

115
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:55,590
Tell me your wish.

116
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,190
If I must name one,

117
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,430
then I wish the benches in the yamen

118
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:09,630
were a little taller,

119
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:11,430
just enough to sit comfortably.

120
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:15,360
As you wish.

121
00:07:26,770 --> 00:07:27,770
What's wrong, Hu?

122
00:07:28,870 --> 00:07:30,360
If your legs were broken,

123
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:33,360
the benches would be taller.

124
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,720
The benches would be taller.

125
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,430
Hu?

126
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:44,600
If your legs were broken,
the benches would be taller.

127
00:07:48,530 --> 00:07:49,680
Hu, wake up!

128
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:56,159
If your legs were broken,
the benches would be taller.

129
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:18,600
Hu.

130
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,660
Still conscious, Young Magistrate?

131
00:08:29,270 --> 00:08:31,120
You're tougher than I expected.

132
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:34,840
So those two murder cases

133
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,320
were your doing?

134
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:40,440
Interesting.

135
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,299
Very interesting.

136
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:44,480
You speak of benches and chairs,

137
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,720
yet that isn't your true desire.

138
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,490
What you really want

139
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:52,030
is to find the missing half

140
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:52,960
of Liu Fufeng's heart,

141
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,870
right?

142
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:57,000
Don't worry.

143
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,630
Such a sincere wish,

144
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,270
I will definitely fulfill it for you.

145
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:28,670
My Lady.

146
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,720
My Lady, what are you doing?

147
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,600
Saving your life.

148
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:38,440
But...

149
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,550
but your spiritual power...

150
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:45,880
You shouldn't be wasting it on me anymore.

151
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,270
Behave.

152
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,670
My Lady.

153
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,120
Are you

154
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,680
starting to believe me now?

155
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:14,360
Lady Fufeng,

156
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,440
does it hurt

157
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,570
losing half your heart?

158
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:26,380
I don't want to see you suffer.

159
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:33,240
Lady Fufeng, I...

160
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:34,840
Sleep.

161
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:06,270
Get up.

162
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,850
Stop playing dead.

163
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:09,160
I know you're awake.

164
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:13,030
Which arm is hurt?

165
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,600
Ouch, ouch!

166
00:11:40,030 --> 00:11:40,960
Feeling better?

167
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:44,160
Drink the medicine.

168
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:49,920
Did you make this yourself?

169
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:55,330
Did you make it just for me?

170
00:11:55,490 --> 00:11:57,020
Stop talking nonsense!

171
00:11:57,230 --> 00:11:57,600
Just drink!

172
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,400
I'll drink it!

173
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:07,800
Feeling better?

174
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,550
Thank you, Fengling.

175
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,720
If there's a next time...

176
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,910
There won't be a next time.

177
00:12:18,250 --> 00:12:19,130
Silly.

178
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,240
I mean,

179
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,340
if there's a next time,

180
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,840
send someone else to save me.

181
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:39,510
Lady Fufeng,

182
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,720
about that demon in white...

183
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:45,080
You should be
worrying about yourself first.

184
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:53,610
Thank you, My Lady.

185
00:12:57,270 --> 00:12:58,670
Let me ask you something.

186
00:12:58,720 --> 00:13:01,200
Yesterday, did you make any kind of wish,

187
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,600
or have a passing thought

188
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,480
while facing that demon?

189
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,390
He did ask me to make a wish,

190
00:13:08,530 --> 00:13:10,170
but I didn't know what he was,

191
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:12,610
I just said something to brush him off.

192
00:13:12,870 --> 00:13:16,600
I said I wished the benches in the yamen

193
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:17,860
were a little taller.

194
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:22,480
Thank goodness.

195
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:25,910
My Lady,

196
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,750
what exactly is that demon?

197
00:13:30,870 --> 00:13:31,870
He's a

198
00:13:32,790 --> 00:13:34,470
troublesome Wish Fox.

199
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:36,960
He feeds on wishes

200
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,680
and is evil by nature.

201
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:41,580
He can pry into the deepest

202
00:13:41,610 --> 00:13:43,440
and strongest desires of the human heart,

203
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,870
then fulfill them

204
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,320
in the most twisted and extreme way,

205
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,120
and draw power from it.

206
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:53,750
I thought Li Mao
and Ji were harmed by Bai Han.

207
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:58,440
I never expected
it was because this Wish Fox escaped.

208
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:01,630
His demonic power isn't strong,

209
00:14:02,170 --> 00:14:05,170
but he's skilled
at exploiting people's weaknesses.

210
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:06,450
Yesterday,

211
00:14:07,470 --> 00:14:09,000
did he say anything to you?

212
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:13,000
What you want

213
00:14:14,390 --> 00:14:16,550
is to find the missing half

214
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:17,670
of Liu Fufeng's heart,

215
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:18,510
right?

216
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,850
What are you talking about?

217
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:28,730
No wonder...

218
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,750
her presence lingers on you.

219
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,000
Just as I thought.

220
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:36,870
Just as I thought.

221
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:41,000
Her heart is beating inside you.

222
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,710
Can't you feel it?

223
00:14:44,790 --> 00:14:46,190
Can't you feel her warmth

224
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:47,920
and her pain?

225
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,000
Nothing.

226
00:14:59,670 --> 00:15:00,630
Lord Bai,

227
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:05,120
don't let anyone control your heart.

228
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,390
This is mine.

229
00:15:35,630 --> 00:15:36,360
Lady Fufeng,

230
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,730
Lady Fufeng,

231
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:43,550
Lady Fufeng,

232
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,550
I just ran into Fengling outside,

233
00:15:45,550 --> 00:15:46,240
so I figured,

234
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:48,840
you must've been worried
about Lord Bai and me.

235
00:15:48,910 --> 00:15:50,510
Thank you for saving my life.

236
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:52,050
But speaking of which,

237
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:53,880
Lord Bai, you are really lucky.

238
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:55,480
You fell from such a height

239
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,670
and came away completely unharmed.

240
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:59,200
Your injuries aren't even
as serious as mine.

241
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,270
It's all thanks to

242
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:04,690
Lady Fufeng using her
spiritual power to heal me.

243
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,200
How is that possible?

244
00:16:07,550 --> 00:16:09,320
Lady Fufeng's demonic spiritual power

245
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:11,080
can't heal a mortal's wounds.

246
00:16:11,370 --> 00:16:13,080
If it were forcibly transferred,

247
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:14,600
at best, it would damage your meridians;

248
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:16,030
at worst, your body
would explode and you'd die.

249
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:17,120
That's common knowledge.

250
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,900
You were probably just lucky.

251
00:16:18,980 --> 00:16:19,710
When you fell,

252
00:16:19,710 --> 00:16:21,240
you must be caught by a tree.

253
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:25,630
Don't flatter yourself.

254
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:26,840
Claiming Lady Fufeng saved you?

255
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,600
-Don't you feel ashamed?
-Enough.

256
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:30,530
There's no point dwelling on this.

257
00:16:31,330 --> 00:16:32,260
What matters now

258
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:34,030
is finding the Wish Fox quickly,

259
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:35,440
and bringing him to justice.

260
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,910
First thing tomorrow morning,

261
00:16:36,910 --> 00:16:38,240
I will pay Li Mao a visit.

262
00:16:38,870 --> 00:16:39,600
Yes, My Lady.

263
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:40,640
Understood.

264
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:53,600
Lord Bai.

265
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:55,510
I'm sorry.

266
00:16:59,910 --> 00:17:01,790
My Lord, do you no longer mind

267
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:04,619
that the benches
in our county yamen are too short?

268
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:10,310
You don't want to soar in the sky,

269
00:17:10,589 --> 00:17:11,160
do you?

270
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,220
It hurts! It hurts!

271
00:17:15,730 --> 00:17:18,140
[Xiqianhua Mansion]

272
00:17:25,510 --> 00:17:26,349
Lady Fufeng.

273
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,240
Lord Bai.

274
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,920
Have you found
the scholar from the ruined temple?

275
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:31,440
He can prove my innocence.

276
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:33,700
He can also prove I never left that night.

277
00:17:33,720 --> 00:17:34,510
I...

278
00:17:35,310 --> 00:17:37,350
When can I go home?

279
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,560
My mother must be worried sick.

280
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:42,110
Li Mao, think carefully.

281
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:44,350
That day at the ruined temple,

282
00:17:44,350 --> 00:17:46,750
what exactly did you say to that scholar?

283
00:17:51,350 --> 00:17:53,240
I was very drunk back then.

284
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:56,570
There are a lot I can't remember clearly.

285
00:17:58,480 --> 00:18:02,000
I only remember feeling suffocated inside.

286
00:18:03,030 --> 00:18:03,830
It seems

287
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:07,880
I poured my heart out to him.

288
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,880
How pitiful.

289
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:13,790
This world has treated you too cruelly!

290
00:18:15,790 --> 00:18:16,640
But it's okay.

291
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:18,590
Tell me,

292
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:22,120
what do you desire most
deep down in your heart?

293
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:24,680
What is your truest wish?

294
00:18:25,980 --> 00:18:26,930
Wish?

295
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:31,680
I...

296
00:18:32,950 --> 00:18:35,990
I don't want them to bully me anymore.

297
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:40,550
And I don't want my mother
to suffer anymore.

298
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:45,880
Then, do you need my help?

299
00:18:48,670 --> 00:18:50,710
You want to help me?

300
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:59,750
Are you really willing to help me?

301
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:04,070
When it comes to granting wishes,

302
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:05,880
I have never failed.

303
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:19,200
My Lord, My Lady.

304
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:20,030
Did I...

305
00:19:21,040 --> 00:19:23,000
did I say something wrong?

306
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:40,590
Mother!

307
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:43,350
Mother!

308
00:19:43,350 --> 00:19:45,830
My Lady, I...

309
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:48,270
What is it?

310
00:19:48,510 --> 00:19:50,510
Mother!

311
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:53,790
My Lady, I lied to you.

312
00:19:58,070 --> 00:20:00,260
The Wish Fox discovered my wish,

313
00:20:00,290 --> 00:20:01,590
and it wasn't about the benches—

314
00:20:01,590 --> 00:20:04,160
it was hoping you could
find the missing half of your heart.

315
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:05,160
Seeing Li Mao just now

316
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,690
made me realize something.

317
00:20:07,060 --> 00:20:08,790
If he really helped fulfill my wish,

318
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:10,390
would that put you in danger?

319
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,570
What else did he say?

320
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:15,880
He...

321
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,640
He looked at my chest

322
00:20:21,070 --> 00:20:23,680
and said the heart is inside me.

323
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,720
I... I don't know what he meant by that.

